tip.text: Interrior,breakfast,location and service is good too and just near sun suria mall and jesselton

Goreng pisang and rojak ayam so nice
The chicken porridge's nice..with strawberry chiller..the bad thing is that they don't have low fat/skim milk for coffee :/
Strawberry tart is SO good!Also the peach tart..
Bathrooms clean..service is great..pantry is clean too and you'd have a great view as well
Minimum 1 hour cuddle time with cats for $12/pax...so pricey
Nothing actually superbly nice tht would actually make me wanna Queue..i tried the iced choc & carbonara..mediocre
